query:
SELECT 
  p.id, 
  p.sku, 
  p.tenantId,
  t.name as tenantName,
  p.description
FROM products p
LEFT JOIN tenants t ON p.tenantId = t.id
WHERE p.sku = '401460P'
ORDER BY p.id;
